original_prompt: Extract named entities and classify the tokens a under one of the following labels [I-LOC, B-ORG, O, B-PER, I-PER, I-MISC, B-MISC, I-ORG, B-LOC]. The format should be ["Token": "India", "NER_tag": "B-LOC", ..., ...]
optimized_prompt: Transform the provided raw input text into structured named entity recognition (NER) outputs. For each token in the input, classify it into one of the specified labels such as PERSON, ORGANIZATION, LOCATION, DATE, etc. Format the output as a list of dictionaries where each dictionary contains the token and its corresponding NER tag in the following structure: `{"Token": "<token_value>", "NER_tag": "<label>"}`. Ensure that all tokens are included and classified accurately based on their respective categories, maintaining the sequence of tokens from the input.
